    "name": "Winter Survival - 冬日幸存者",
    "steam_appid": 1394960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/d81aa0e85d9adfbf955aee248dd893bb.avif?t=1764318067\" width=781 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三种不同游戏模式</strong>- 剧情模式、生存模式与寒潮模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情驱动的生存体验，</strong>专为希望从全新视角重新探索该类型的新老玩家打造</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>理智系统考验你的游戏策略，</strong>彻底颠覆难度梯度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高度自定义体验</strong> - 打造专属游戏玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态环境</strong>随你的进程不断演变，持续提升挑战难度</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/967453c0194903b7f090fb336bee1373.avif?t=1764318067\" width=781 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《冬日幸存者》</strong>融合经典生存机制、心理张力与叙事悬疑。在<strong>剧情模式</strong>中，揭开丹尼的故事 - 他是一名新手，唯一的愿望就是回家。学习我们生存玩法中的基础与高级机制，并为丹尼的未来负责。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在沙盒式<strong>生存模式</strong>中走出属于自己的道路，不受叙事限制。按照自己的喜好定制玩法，从不同的初始场景中选择，打造属于你自己的生存冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或者尝试<strong>寒潮模式</strong> - 一种可快速加入、随时退出的生存体验，死亡始终离你只有一步之遥。尽可能长时间生存下来，收集越多金条越好，最终与其他生存者比拼分数。每一轮挑战都会带来宝贵的知识和更优质的初始装备，有可能助你获得更高分数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/3cd2dcfff01db885546d9fba2e0ae4d7.avif?t=1764318067\" width=780 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/d41654661d92086026451aadbc15adfd.avif?t=1764318067\" width=781 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/de30f41f89d7f309f6c202f260caa11f.poster.avif?t=1764318067\" width=780 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/de30f41f89d7f309f6c202f260caa11f.webm?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/de30f41f89d7f309f6c202f260caa11f.mp4?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >理智是你最脆弱的资源。当饥饿侵袭、孤独感加剧，掠食者在夜间潜行，随着创伤值不断升高，你对现实的掌控开始松动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幻觉、恐慌，甚至臆想中的掠食者，都会变得与狼或冻伤同样危险。而这仅仅是你必须谨慎应对的诸多症状中的冰山一角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/f4e61de1963e4719d99445a252195a7a.avif?t=1764318067\" width=781 height=126 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/aeeb650e73e083fddd75b0a80b0250f4.poster.avif?t=1764318067\" width=780 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/aeeb650e73e083fddd75b0a80b0250f4.webm?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/aeeb650e73e083fddd75b0a80b0250f4.mp4?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作工具、搭建避难所，探索《冬日幸存者》中广阔而充满生机的世界。但请记住- 你在这里只是个外来者。适应荒野，做好应对意外的准备，见证大自然对你的一举一动做出反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/660cb68bc8b8948604a4a5691154ebd8.avif?t=1764318067\" width=781 height=126 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/b0c5f7c23a7270b61f15a13c1aceb97c.poster.avif?t=1764318067\" width=780 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/b0c5f7c23a7270b61f15a13c1aceb97c.webm?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/b0c5f7c23a7270b61f15a13c1aceb97c.mp4?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >广阔开放世界任你探索 - 踏足冰封森林、湿润沼泽、废弃聚落，以及寂静得令人窒息的幽暗洞穴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >静悄悄地移动以躲避危险，利用地形智取掠食者，或与它们正面交锋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/a950a40c9caa9c85f316ab125f1a1821.avif?t=1764318067\" width=781 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/7a400d7474aab5eea61864a6491a1cb3.poster.avif?t=1764318067\" width=780 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/7a400d7474aab5eea61864a6491a1cb3.webm?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1394960/extras/7a400d7474aab5eea61864a6491a1cb3.mp4?t=1764318067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《冬日幸存者》为你呈现生存玩法的基础与高级机制，但融入了我们独特的设计。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正在寻找物资或食物？搜寻周边区域，或是选择更危险的方式 - 尝试从狼那里夺取。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快要冻僵？生起篝火或许是你真正的救赎。火焰会为你提供温暖、驱赶狼群，但也可能吸引其他掠食者 - 尤其是在野外烹饪时。 <br><br>想猎杀那只在这片区域出没的鹿？没问题，但要迅速行动，在其他危险得多的生物对其下手前，抢占这份美味的食物。</p>",
